Interface OnGetRequestDataListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DriverBrowsingActivity, DriverOnGoingActivity, DriverPickUpActivity, DriverScanActivity, Login, RiderConfirmRiderActivity, RiderMatchingActivity, RiderOnGoingRequestActivity, RiderReviewActivity, RiderWaitingRideActivity

    public interface OnGetRequestDataListener
    This is the interface that act as a listener when interacting with firebase so that it can be notified when requests data transfer is successful or failed.
